(494, 'AI notes: Skydo''s founder Movin shared insights about their experience as an early customer of TruFides, an AI startup in the compliance and fraud detection space. This conversation provided valuable feedback about TruFides'' product, founders, and market positioning for a potential investor. Background and Relationship: - Movin knew Devang (TruFides co-founder) from PhonePe where Movin hired the first batch of APMs - Skydo became TruFides'' first non-crypto customer about a year ago - Implementation occurred approximately 4-5 months ago - Skydo pays about ₹80K (1/10th the cost of a compliance team member at ₹8L CTC) Problem and Solution: - Cross-border payments face money laundering risks requiring negative media screening - Traditional process: Compliance team manually reviews negative media articles - TruFides solution: AI reads articles and extracts key information to: - Disambiguate identities (is it the same person?) - Assess crime seriousness and transaction relevance - Reduce review time from 10 minutes to 10 seconds per case Results and Impact: - Solution "works beautifully" as Skydo''s "first AI win" - Saves approximately one full-time compliance person - Compliance head is satisfied with the implementation - Became a precedent for other AI adoption within Skydo Competitive Assessment: - TruFides vs. Fravity (Elevation Capital investment): - TruFides was immediately focused on a specific use case - Fravity was "all over the place" initially with too many use cases - Fr...'),
(499, 'Investment note from @Anonymous 2025-05-14T12:23:00.000+05:30: Sharing the note for our $30K investment in UGX.AI as part of their angel round of $547K at $4.4M post-money. This should amount to ~0.69% ownership at conversion. Venture Partner: Ramakant Sharma DeVC Collective: Utsav Somani, Manish Agarwal Other angels include Asad (Lambdatest), Loveleen Bhatia (Edureka), Prateek Maheshwari (Physicswallah) and Mihir/Ravish from PointOne capital. Investing Process: - Cash got the lead from RK and did the 1PE - Ran a quick 2PE with the full DeVC team and also socialized the thesis/opportunity with members like Vasant (OfB) and PeerCapital. - We did BRCs on the key founder and realised that they are out of domain and strategic thinking could be a big gap hence only warrant a 30K community top-up basis the excitement from the collective (2+ collective member commit criteria) About the Company UGX.AI is building a full-stack Industrial DataOps platform to enable manufacturing companies to access and leverage real-time machine data for productivity, cost efficiency, and sustainability improvements. They provide an integrated hardware, middleware, and software platform including: 1. Universal Edge Gateway: Low-cost, industrial-grade device for machine connectivity. 1. Industrial Protocol Library: Supports 40+ machine models, converting complex machine protocols into software-friendly APIs. 1. Unified Industrial Data Platform: Transforms machine data into actionable insights. 1. Indust...'),
